data.title: CommQuest Services: Revenue, Competitors, Alternatives
data.meta_description: CommQuest Services top competitors are Franklin County Job and Family, Women's Recovery Center and Butler County Board of Developmental Disabilities and they have annual revenue of $25.4M  and 231  employees.
data.text:
CommQuest Services is one of the largest addiction, mental health, and social service organizations in Ohio. We provide a continuum of care to more than 20,000 clients on an annual basis.
